      <figure><figure><img src="/assets/images/products/pressure-cooker/kelebihan-multicooker-cuckoo-goreng.jpg" alt="kelebihan multicooker cuckoo" loading="lazy" /><figcaption>kelebihan multicooker cuckoo</figcaption></figure><figcaption><strong>Goreng Sosej &amp; Popia</strong> - <em>Sumber Gambar: Fadzli Rosli</em></figcaption></figure>
      
