      <h2><strong>CUCKOO MULTICOOKER</strong></h2>
      
      <h2><strong>P10</strong></h2>
      
      <figure><figure><img src="/assets/images/misc/poster-produk-cuckoo-a4.016.png" alt="CUCKOO POSTER PAMPHLET PRICE INFO - P10 MULTICOOKER" loading="lazy" /><figcaption>CUCKOO POSTER PAMPHLET PRICE INFO - P10 MULTICOOKER</figcaption></figure></figure>
      
      <p>Cuckoo P10 Multicooker adalah periuk Cuckoo yang terbaru dalam pasaran Malaysia. </p>
      
